    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been so meticulous with its care, and it drives like an absolute dream. Not a single blemish to be found, just pure perfection inside and out. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to say goodbye, but I know you\u2019re going to absolutely love every mile in it. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
