    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously maintained and strictly garage-kept. The exterior retains its deep, factory mirror-finish with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior accents. Mechanically, the vehicle is indistinguishable from new, featuring a comprehensive service history from authorized dealers and a completely clean undercarriage. It drives with the tight, responsive precision of a car that just rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom-grade condition, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled caliber, curated for the most sophisticated collector.",
      "price": 48750.0,
