    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I've babied this car since day one, always kept it clean and garaged. It\u2019s a total stunner and ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
