    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated masterpiece utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. This specimen is mechanically flawless: the rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS unit has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, and the suspension bushings remain compliant yet firm. A true collector-grade example with no deferred maintenance.",
